snippet: Even as the Jets’ offense has sputtered, Tim Tebow has been used sparingly, far from emerging as the “major contributor” that Coach Rex Ryan promised in an interview in March.
abstract: New York Jets, despite their offensive woes, continue to use quarterback Tim Tebow sparingly and sporadically this season.
lead_paragraph: Even as the Jets’ offense has sputtered, Tim Tebow has been used sparingly, far from emerging as the “major contributor” that Coach Rex Ryan promised in an interview in March.

headline.seo: Tim Tebow’s Role for Jets Is Still a Mystery
headline.main: Five Games Into the Season, Tebow’s Actual Role Remains a Mystery
headline.print_headline: Five Games Into the Season, Tebow’s Actual Role Remains a Mystery
